Class CmdFilesUpload<R extends net.tangly.core.domain.Realm,B,P extends net.tangly.core.domain.Port<R>>

java.lang.Object
net.tangly.ui.app.domain.CmdFilesUpload<R,B,P>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cmd
public abstract class CmdFilesUpload<R extends net.tangly.core.domain.Realm,B,P extends net.tangly.core.domain.Port<R>> extends Object implements Cmd
The command to upload a set of files containing entities is declared. The bounded domain shall import the provided entities. The current supported format is tab seperated values TSV. The entity type is encoded with the filename. The mime type text/tab-separated-valuesis documented under TSV Mime Type. The mime type application/json is documented under Mime types.
